            <sentence id="6.1">Reproducible: Always</sentence>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph id="7">
            <sentence id="7.1">Steps to Reproduce:</sentence>
            <sentence id="7.2">1 invoke firefox with 2 urls set as the home page "http://www.msn.com/|http://hp-desktop.aol.com/"</sentence>
            <sentence id="7.3">2 press the homepage button</sentence>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph id="8">
            <sentence id="8.1">Actual Results:
